Package: mastrShiny
Title: Click-and-Run Shiny Dashboards for the German Marktstammdatenregister
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("mastr-shiny", "contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: A collection of bslib-styled Shiny dashboards that visualize the
    Bundesnetzagentur Marktstammdatenregister (MaStR) by reading
    pre-processed Parquet files from GitHub Releases through DuckDB's httpfs
    extension. End users never need to download the ~2.8 GB XML dump.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
Imports:
    shiny (>= 1.8),
    bslib (>= 0.7),
    DBI,
    duckdb (>= 0.10),
    httr2,
    memoise,
    rlang,
    plotly,
    leaflet,
    reactable,
    viridisLite,
    dplyr
Suggests:
    shinylive,
    renv,
    testthat (>= 3.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
